---
title: Writing - Francis Rubio
description: Articles, musings, and anything I just thought to write about
pagination:
  data: collections.posts
  size: 8
  reverse: true
permalink: /writing/{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}{{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }}/{% endif %}index.html
activePath: writing
---
<section class="padding--xl" aria-labelledby="section-heading-4" style="width: min(100ch, 90%); margin-inline: auto;">
  <div class="stack margin-bottom--xl">
    <span id="section-heading-4" class="uppercase ls-l font-sans">Writing</span>
    <h1 class="font-serif responsive">The Life and Times of Francis Rubio</h1>
    <p>A glimpse of what it's like to be me.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="tag-scroller">
    {% for item in collections.postTags %}
      <a href="/writing/categories/{{ item }}/" class="tag" style="width: fit-content;">{{ item }}</a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  {% set collection = pagination.items %}
  {% include 'components/post-grid.njk' %}
</section>

<div class="center-justified cluster padding--l">
  {% if pagination.href.previous %}
    <a href="{{ pagination.href.previous }}" class="button">Previous</a>
  {% endif %}

  {% if pagination.href.next %}
    <a href="{{ pagination.href.next }}" class="button">Next</a>
  {% endif %}
</div>

<footer class="stack gap--xl m-block--xxxl" style="text-align: center; margin-inline: auto; width: min(var(--content-width), 90%);">
  <div class="section__header">
    <hgroup role="group">
      <h2 class="section__subtitle fs-3">Follow me on the Fediverse</h2>
      <p style="text-align: left;">If you were impressed by my mind because of these longform texts, I encourage you to follow me on Mastodon and see my silly side. (I talk about all kinds of things, though, so be prepared for that.)</p>
    </hgroup>
  </div>
  <div class="stack ai--center gap--s">
    <a href="{{ site.contact.mastodon.url }}" class="primary button" target="blank" rel="noopener">
      {{ "user-plus" | icon | safe }}
      <span>Follow me on Mastodon</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</footer>